						               													<description>The Triangle Challenge - A Game of Strategy &amp;amp; Daring&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The object for each player is to score the most points by creating triangles where all three end-points match the color of their wooden stacker.  The larger the triangle, the larger the point value.  The player with the most points after all 20 discs have been played, wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Strategy - Strategy is the key to secretly loading your wooden stacker and selecting which move to make on every turn.  Each player controls 5 red and 5 blue discs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Dare - Daring is essential to out-fox your opponent on every turn.  Try to bluff and trick your opponent into helping you create more triangles of your color to win, without letting yourself be fooled.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents:  Wooden game board, two wooden stackers, twenty discs (10 blue, 10 red), instructions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
